{"tid":1385363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想幫手助養貧窮兒童、和理非入","createTime":"2019-07-30T05:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:07:32.000Z","uid":163685,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dd637acfa6863d555a1775e145828b8a30b9b016","tid":1385363,"uid":163685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:14:41.000Z","msg":"其實比起大家買埋啲咩卷乜卷<br />\n前線更加需要嘅係高級裝備同埋人手！<br />\n你地提供裝 我地前線唔洗不停課金買裝 咪有錢買飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都理解有好多人有唔同原因出唔到黎前線<br />\n所以建議大家除左課金買裝<br />\n仲有一樣野大家可以做：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">就係做回收兵！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n強烈建議大家於每次郊遊接近尾聲個陣<br />\n著得有幾街坊就幾街坊 <br />\n甚至扮大陸人鳩嗚 <br />\n攞大袋或者師奶買餸手推車<br />\n落附近地鐵站<br />\n黎回收貴重野餐物資 ，話曬都好多小朋友唔敢帶裝走<br />\n咁就由公正守法嘅大家帶走（帶防具行街無犯法嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再係下次郊遊帶番去物資站<br />\n<br />\n成個過程合法又環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n清潔香港，人人都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9230d727fbffa3f22541d54d7d32b73a28d4da","tid":1385363,"uid":163685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:15:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92d38fd4bf7862ef677b6da047254b4db12421b7","tid":1385363,"uid":163685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:15:43.000Z","msg":"再推推"},{"pid":"d1d1ba1d41af5600dce8cf4281d80a2f4c6f75ff","tid":1385363,"uid":163685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:16:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4e55d0621445803b3c15aaaa7076803f8a384e1","tid":1385363,"uid":109794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:16:36.000Z","msg":"推!!<br />\nBTW<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請入 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dsPmtT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dsPmtT</a> 幫手推post!!<br />\n一齊report 9 藍絲 fb pages, 斷佢地輿論!!!!!<br />\n一人一Report, 搞到佢地摺埋!!!!<br />